name: sartje the bikergirl
description:
She was an undercover agent 
for BIN, her maintask was uncovering any 
case of child trafficking in this city
she always wore frangipani flowers on her helmet.
As in Hinduism, frangipani can be interpreted as 
dedication and devotion. 
While in Buddhism, this flower means a symbol of immortality.  
Perhaps there is more...
